extends layout

block content
  .min-h-screen.flex.items-center.justify-center.bg-gray-100
    .bg-white.rounded-2xl.shadow-md.p-8.w-full.max-w-sm
      h2.text-2xl.font-bold.text-center.text-gray-800.mb-6 회원가입

      if error
        p.text-sm.text-red-500.mb-4.text-center= error

      form(action='/auth/register', method='POST')
        .mb-4
          label.block.text-sm.font-medium.text-gray-700.mb-1(for='name') 이름
          input#name(
            type='text',
            name='name',
            placeholder='이름을 입력하세요',
            required,
            class='w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400'
          )
        .mb-4
          label.block.text-sm.font-medium.text-gray-700.mb-1(for='studentId') 학번
          input#studentId(
            type='text',
            name='studentId',
            placeholder='학번을 입력하세요',
            required,
            class='w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400'
          )
        .mb-4
          label.block.text-sm.font-medium.text-gray-700.mb-1(for='username') 아이디
          input#username(
            type='text',
            name='username',
            placeholder='아이디를 입력하세요',
            required,
            class='w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400'
          )
        .mb-6
          label.block.text-sm.font-medium.text-gray-700.mb-1(for='password') 비밀번호
          input#password(
            type='password',
            name='password',
            placeholder='비밀번호를 입력하세요',
            required,
            class='w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400'
          )
        button.w-full.font-semibold.py-2.rounded-lg.transition(
          type='submit',
          class='bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white'
        ) 회원가입

      p.text-sm.text-center.text-gray-500.mt-4
        | 이미 계정이 있으신가요?&nbsp;
        a(href='/auth/login', class='text-blue-500 hover:underline') 로그인
